---
title: Zesty Clementine Tomato Panzanella Serves 1 | with Ciabatta and Marinated Bocconcini
description: A burst of sunshine on a rainy spring day! This twist on an Italian classic features beefsteak tomatoes, juicy clementines, toasted ciabatta and crisp spring mix, all tossed with briny pickled shallots for the perfect acidic punch!
